data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This beautiful 3,200 sq ft residence nestled in Sandcreek Estates, features custom finishes and impeccable attention to detail throughout. Step inside and experience the spacious and open floor plan coupled with high ceilings connecting the living room and kitchen, creating the perfect atmosphere for entertaining guests or spending quality time with family. As you explore the 5 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, you'll find that the same level of attention to detail has been extended throughout the home. The three-car garage provides ample space for parking and storage. Plus a spot to put your RV. Whether you're enjoying the ambiance of the fireplace, working in the well-appointed office, or entertaining in the expansive family room, this home seamlessly combines style and functionality for modern living. Call for your private showing today!
